            "text": "The Heir Affair"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " by Heather Cocks. This is the second book in "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "em"
              }
            ],
            "text": "The Royal We"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " series. It was good, but I found the beginning and middle to be very slow. The ending made up for it so I finished it feeling like it was a solid fiction read. It's been a long time since I read the first book in "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "em"
              }
            ],
            "text": "The Royal We"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " series, but I remember LOVING that one, so the slow start for this one was a little disappointing."
          }
